Requirements:

  xattr     http://undefined.org/python/#xattr
              or 
            easy_install xattr

  pyfuse    http://code.google.com/p/fusepy/
              or
            easy_install pyfuse

Special OSX Requirements:

  macfuse for most OSX systems:
    http://code.google.com/p/macfuse/

  macfuse for Snow Leopard 64 Bit:
    http://caurea.org/2009/09/15/unofficial-macfuse-release-for-64bit-kernels/
      or
    http://github.com/wereHamster/macfuse

